{"tid":1697244,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】領展CCTV有一個重大疑點！","createTime":"2019-11-06T17:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T11:42:20.000Z","uid":266060,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e56c0285a3c57f0450dc3268c02a13c015abe27c","tid":1697244,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:04:06.000Z","msg":"C31<br />\n01:02:12 - 01:02:17<br />\n一個疑似黑衫黑褲黑背囊嘅男子上3樓左轉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yg5dTeh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYg5dTeh.png&h=1b7ca964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到01:02:28為止，個Cam都影到斜路口，\b唔見呢個人折返或轉另一邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDNov1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDNov1e.png&h=e5c36488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n01:02:47有一個人由2樓落斜，但佢背向2樓、行路中間，唔似由3樓轉彎落嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HrktG8w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrktG8w.png&h=d84a9323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁佢去咗邊呢？睇3樓CCTV<br />\nC35<br />\n呢個人上到3樓時係01:02:17，當時Cam唔係影住斜路口，而係轉咗去lift口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DZqKny.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DZqKny.png&h=cbcaf1bd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n支Cam轉到最盡，都仲見到lift口，所以肯定佢冇搭lift走<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZHjOPv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZHjOPv.png&h=7bb04a05&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n轉返去斜路口嗰邊，完全唔見佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9hWQ25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9hWQ25.png&h=c575e5b6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且根據C34<br />\n01:02:58消防已出lift到3樓，唔見呢個人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WneNXDS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWneNXDS.png&h=582b4216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能性得3個<br />\n1) 呢個人喺01:02:28-01:02:42呢短短14秒突然轉咗右或折返，剛好冇任何cam影到<br />\n2) C31由2樓落斜嗰個人真係佢<br />\n3) 佢墮下<br />\n<br />\n應該冇其他可能？"},{"pid":"4c87bd9bb3edb63a66c44a82ceffa2d0ec511b07","tid":1697244,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"想放棄想輸，入嚟聽完首歌再決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aec8076ae41dfd4eb9e664d474b478c4fbd8a30c","tid":1697244,"uid":94537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:09:13.000Z","msg":"細心樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推一推"},{"pid":"2ed95ddadbc7e4f943778d4c11d3219065a19f41","tid":1697244,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:09:38.000Z","msg":"[米豬連] 十八區黃店自發組米豬連聯盟 可由出名黃店牽頭(渣哥/龍門/一芳/水門) 互相提供優惠/請手足工作!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697221</a><br />\n<br />\n超突發! 食完藍絲/紅底野食肚痛肚屙到要SL! 老豆老母驚左話以後唔買! 肚痛師!?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697220</a>"},{"pid":"18c747fdf161ea008c79770e47dd498d56edcd53","tid":1697244,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76aca7cc47d2c4b9ab26e778bbc37f45c6432acb","tid":1697244,"uid":202876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d40bdd482e30b60ca4a1afdf627abf0244d0c8f","tid":1697244,"uid":295670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:15:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44cf23e1f4985501c6eac08b19d3558a835c8f84","tid":1697244,"uid":1643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"其實有冇可能根本冇墮樓呢回事，而係其他成因做成？"},{"pid":"ba52528d107cd